**Type of Compound**  
* nicotine - alkaloid  
* morphine - alkaloid  
:* Alkaloids are a group of nitrogenous organic compounds that have physiological effects on humans
* procaine - local anesthetic (Synthetic organic compound)  
* Botulinum toxin - protein: chain of amino-acid residues joined by peptide bonds  
  
